This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=4094

Show vim tips everytime when you enter vim. 

Screenshot:https://github.com/downloads/yesmeck/tips.vim/screenshot.png 

**Requirement** 

ruby 

**Usage** 

Just open your vim! Or use command ``:NextTips`` to view more tips. 

Your can submit your tips to http://vim-tips.org 
